messageBody:
Hi friends,
I have a doubt and I believe that you people can help me.

My questions are:
1) Does junit support EJB?

2)Does junit support RMI?

3)I have a method that returns a javabean object.The method works
fine else where but, when invoked in the test case it returns a
null.What could be wrong?

I request you to take a few seconds to answer these
questions.
Thanking you.
Sincerely,
Sreedevi Giridhar.
